4374 rd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, &sum_rdc, subsize,
4375 pc_tree->leaf_split[0], best_rdc.rate, best_rdc.dist);
4376 if (sum_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
4377 sum_rdc.rdcost = INT64_MAX;
4378 } else {
4379 if (cpi->sf.prune_ref_frame_for_rect_partitions) {
4380 const int ref1 = pc_tree->leaf_split[0]->mic.ref_frame[0];
4381 const int ref2 = pc_tree->leaf_split[0]->mic.ref_frame[1];
4382 for (i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
4383 ref_frames_used[i] |= (1 << ref1);
4384 if (ref2 > 0) ref_frames_used[i] |= (1 << ref2);
4385 }
4386 }
4387 }
4388 } else {
4389 for (i = 0; (i < 4) && ((sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) || must_split);
4390 ++i) {
4391 const int x_idx = (i & 1) * mi_step;
4392 const int y_idx = (i >> 1) * mi_step;
4393 int found_best_rd = 0;
4394 RD_COST best_rdc_split;
4395 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&best_rdc_split);
4396
4397 if (best_rdc.rate < INT_MAX && best_rdc.dist < INT64_MAX) {
4398 // A must split test here increases the number of sub
4399 // partitions but hurts metrics results quite a bit,
4400 // so this extra test is commented out pending
4401 // further tests on whether it adds much in terms of
4402 // visual quality.
4403 // (must_split) ? best_rdc.rate
4404 // : best_rdc.rate - sum_rdc.rate,
4405 // (must_split) ? best_rdc.dist
4406 // : best_rdc.dist - sum_rdc.dist,
4407 best_rdc_split.rate = best_rdc.rate - sum_rdc.rate;
4408 best_rdc_split.dist = best_rdc.dist - sum_rdc.dist;
4409 }
4410
4411 if (mi_row + y_idx >= cm->mi_rows || mi_col + x_idx >= cm->mi_cols)
4412 continue;
4413
4414 pc_tree->split[i]->index = i;
4415 if (cpi->sf.prune_ref_frame_for_rect_partitions)
4416 pc_tree->split[i]->none.rate = INT_MAX;
4417 found_best_rd = rd_pick_partition(
4418 cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row + y_idx, mi_col + x_idx, subsize,
4419 &this_rdc, best_rdc_split, pc_tree->split[i]);
4420
4421 if (found_best_rd == 0) {
4422 sum_rdc.rdcost = INT64_MAX;
4423 break;
4424 } else {
4425 if (cpi->sf.prune_ref_frame_for_rect_partitions &&
4426 pc_tree->split[i]->none.rate != INT_MAX) {
4427 const int ref1 = pc_tree->split[i]->none.mic.ref_frame[0];
4428 const int ref2 = pc_tree->split[i]->none.mic.ref_frame[1];
4429 ref_frames_used[i] |= (1 << ref1);
4430 if (ref2 > 0) ref_frames_used[i] |= (1 << ref2);
4431 }
4432 sum_rdc.rate += this_rdc.rate;
4433 sum_rdc.dist += this_rdc.dist;
4434 vp9_rd_cost_update(partition_mul, x->rddiv, &sum_rdc);
4435 }
4436 }
4437 }
4438
4439 if (((sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) || must_split) && i == 4) {
4440 sum_rdc.rate += cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_SPLIT];
4441 vp9_rd_cost_update(partition_mul, x->rddiv, &sum_rdc);
4442
4443 if ((sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) ||
4444 (must_split && (sum_rdc.dist < best_rdc.dist))) {
4445 best_rdc = sum_rdc;
4446 should_encode_sb = 1;
4447 pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_SPLIT;
4448
4449 // Rate and distortion based partition search termination clause.
4450 if (!cpi->sf.rd_ml_partition.search_early_termination &&
4451 !x->e_mbd.lossless &&
4452 ((best_rdc.dist < (dist_breakout_thr >> 2)) ||
4453 (best_rdc.dist < dist_breakout_thr &&
4454 best_rdc.rate < rate_breakout_thr))) {
4455 do_rect = 0;
4456 }
4457 }
4458 } else {
4459 // skip rectangular partition test when larger block size
4460 // gives better rd cost
4461 if (cpi->sf.less_rectangular_check &&
4462 (bsize > cpi->sf.use_square_only_thresh_high ||
4463 best_rdc.dist < dist_breakout_thr))
4464 do_rect &= !partition_none_allowed;
4465 }
4466 restore_context(x, mi_row, mi_col, a, l, sa, sl, bsize);
4467 }
4468
4469 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip_ref_frame_mask = 0;
4470 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip_ref_frame_mask = 0;
4471 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip_ref_frame_mask = 0;
4472 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip_ref_frame_mask = 0;
4473 if (cpi->sf.prune_ref_frame_for_rect_partitions) {
4474 uint8_t used_frames;
4475 used_frames = ref_frames_used[0] | ref_frames_used[1];
4476 if (used_frames) {
4477 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip_ref_frame_mask = ~used_frames & 0xff;
4478 }
4479 used_frames = ref_frames_used[2] | ref_frames_used[3];
4480 if (used_frames) {
4481 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip_ref_frame_mask = ~used_frames & 0xff;
4482 }
4483 used_frames = ref_frames_used[0] | ref_frames_used[2];
4484 if (used_frames) {
4485 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip_ref_frame_mask = ~used_frames & 0xff;
4486 }
4487 used_frames = ref_frames_used[1] | ref_frames_used[3];
4488 if (used_frames) {
4489 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip_ref_frame_mask = ~used_frames & 0xff;
4490 }
4491 }
4492
4493 {
4494 const int do_ml_rect_partition_pruning =
4495 !frame_is_intra_only(cm) && !force_horz_split && !force_vert_split &&
4496 (partition_horz_allowed || partition_vert_allowed) && bsize > BLOCK_8X8;
4497 if (do_ml_rect_partition_pruning) {
4498 ml_prune_rect_partition(cpi, x, bsize, pc_tree, &partition_horz_allowed,
4499 &partition_vert_allowed, best_rdc.rdcost);
4500 }
4501 }
4502
4503 // PARTITION_HORZ
4504 if (partition_horz_allowed &&
4505 (do_rect || vp9_active_h_edge(cpi, mi_row, mi_step))) {
4506 const int part_mode_rate = cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_HORZ];
4507 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_HORZ);
4508 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
4509 if (cpi->sf.adaptive_pred_interp_filter && bsize == BLOCK_8X8 &&
4510 partition_none_allowed)
4511 pc_tree->horizontal[0].pred_interp_filter = pred_interp_filter;
4512 rd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, &sum_rdc, subsize,
4513 &pc_tree->horizontal[0], best_rdc.rate - part_mode_rate,
4514 best_rdc.dist);
4515 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < INT64_MAX) {
4516 sum_rdc.rate += part_mode_rate;
4517 vp9_rd_cost_update(partition_mul, x->rddiv, &sum_rdc);
4518 }
4519
4520 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost && mi_row + mi_step < cm->mi_rows &&
4521 bsize > BLOCK_8X8) {
4522 PICK_MODE_CONTEXT *ctx = &pc_tree->horizontal[0];
4523 update_state(cpi, td, ctx, mi_row, mi_col, subsize, 0);
4524 encode_superblock(cpi, td, tp, 0, mi_row, mi_col, subsize, ctx);
4525 if (cpi->sf.adaptive_pred_interp_filter && bsize == BLOCK_8X8 &&
4526 partition_none_allowed)
4527 pc_tree->horizontal[1].pred_interp_filter = pred_interp_filter;
4528 rd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row + mi_step, mi_col, &this_rdc,
4529 subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[1],
4530 best_rdc.rate - sum_rdc.rate,
4531 best_rdc.dist - sum_rdc.dist);
4532 if (this_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
4533 sum_rdc.rdcost = INT64_MAX;
4534 } else {
4535 sum_rdc.rate += this_rdc.rate;
4536 sum_rdc.dist += this_rdc.dist;
4537 vp9_rd_cost_update(partition_mul, x->rddiv, &sum_rdc);
4538 }
4539 }
4540
4541 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) {
4542 best_rdc = sum_rdc;
4543 should_encode_sb = 1;
4544 pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_HORZ;
4545
4546 if (cpi->sf.less_rectangular_check &&
4547 bsize > cpi->sf.use_square_only_thresh_high)
4548 do_rect = 0;
4549 }
4550 restore_context(x, mi_row, mi_col, a, l, sa, sl, bsize);
4551 }
4552
4553 // PARTITION_VERT
4554 if (partition_vert_allowed &&
4555 (do_rect || vp9_active_v_edge(cpi, mi_col, mi_step))) {
4556 const int part_mode_rate = cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_VERT];
4557 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_VERT);
4558 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
4559 if (cpi->sf.adaptive_pred_interp_filter && bsize == BLOCK_8X8 &&
4560 partition_none_allowed)
4561 pc_tree->vertical[0].pred_interp_filter = pred_interp_filter;
4562 rd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, &sum_rdc, subsize,
4563 &pc_tree->vertical[0], best_rdc.rate - part_mode_rate,
4564 best_rdc.dist);
4565 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < INT64_MAX) {
4566 sum_rdc.rate += part_mode_rate;
4567 vp9_rd_cost_update(partition_mul, x->rddiv, &sum_rdc);
4568 }
4569
4570 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost && mi_col + mi_step < cm->mi_cols &&
4571 bsize > BLOCK_8X8) {
4572 update_state(cpi, td, &pc_tree->vertical[0], mi_row, mi_col, subsize, 0);
4573 encode_superblock(cpi, td, tp, 0, mi_row, mi_col, subsize,
4574 &pc_tree->vertical[0]);
4575 if (cpi->sf.adaptive_pred_interp_filter && bsize == BLOCK_8X8 &&
4576 partition_none_allowed)
4577 pc_tree->vertical[1].pred_interp_filter = pred_interp_filter;
4578 rd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col + mi_step, &this_rdc,
4579 subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[1],
4580 best_rdc.rate - sum_rdc.rate,
4581 best_rdc.dist - sum_rdc.dist);
4582 if (this_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
4583 sum_rdc.rdcost = INT64_MAX;
4584 } else {
4585 sum_rdc.rate += this_rdc.rate;
4586 sum_rdc.dist += this_rdc.dist;
4587 vp9_rd_cost_update(partition_mul, x->rddiv, &sum_rdc);
4588 }
4589 }
4590
4591 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) {
4592 best_rdc = sum_rdc;
4593 should_encode_sb = 1;
4594 pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_VERT;
4595 }
4596 restore_context(x, mi_row, mi_col, a, l, sa, sl, bsize);
4597 }
4598
4599 *rd_cost = best_rdc;
4600
4601 if (should_encode_sb && pc_tree->index != 3) {
4602 int output_enabled = (bsize == BLOCK_64X64);
4603 encode_sb(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, output_enabled, bsize,
4604 pc_tree);
4605#if CONFIG_RATE_CTRL
4606 // Store partition, motion vector of the superblock.
4607 if (output_enabled) {
4608 const int num_unit_rows = get_num_unit_4x4(cpi->frame_info.frame_height);
4609 const int num_unit_cols = get_num_unit_4x4(cpi->frame_info.frame_width);
4610 store_superblock_info(pc_tree, cm->mi_grid_visible, cm->mi_stride,
4611 num_4x4_blocks_wide_lookup[BLOCK_64X64],
4612 num_unit_rows, num_unit_cols, mi_row << 1,
4613 mi_col << 1, cpi->partition_info,
4614 cpi->motion_vector_info);
4615 }
4616#endif // CONFIG_RATE_CTRL
4617 }
4618
4619 if (bsize == BLOCK_64X64) {
4620 assert(tp_orig < *tp);
4621 assert(best_rdc.rate < INT_MAX);
4622 assert(best_rdc.dist < INT64_MAX);
4623 } else {
4624 assert(tp_orig == *tp);
4625 }
4626
4627 return should_encode_sb;
4628}
4629
4630static void encode_rd_sb_row(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td,
4631 TileDataEnc *tile_data, int mi_row,
4632 TOKENEXTRA **tp) {
4633 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
4634 TileInfo *const tile_info = &tile_data->tile_info;
4635 MACROBLOCK *const x = &td->mb;
4636 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
4637 SPEED_FEATURES *const sf = &cpi->sf;
4638 const int mi_col_start = tile_info->mi_col_start;
4639 const int mi_col_end = tile_info->mi_col_end;
4640 int mi_col;
4641 const int sb_row = mi_row >> MI_BLOCK_SIZE_LOG2;
4642 const int num_sb_cols =
4643 get_num_cols(tile_data->tile_info, MI_BLOCK_SIZE_LOG2);
4644 int sb_col_in_tile;
4645
4646 // Initialize the left context for the new SB row
4647 memset(&xd->left_context, 0, sizeof(xd->left_context));
4648 memset(xd->left_seg_context, 0, sizeof(xd->left_seg_context));
4649
4650 // Code each SB in the row
4651 for (mi_col = mi_col_start, sb_col_in_tile = 0; mi_col < mi_col_end;
4652 mi_col += MI_BLOCK_SIZE, sb_col_in_tile++) {
4653 const struct segmentation *const seg = &cm->seg;
4654 int dummy_rate;
4655 int64_t dummy_dist;
4656 RD_COST dummy_rdc;
4657 int i;
4658 int seg_skip = 0;
4659 int orig_rdmult = cpi->rd.RDMULT;
4660
4661 const int idx_str = cm->mi_stride * mi_row + mi_col;
4662 MODE_INFO **mi = cm->mi_grid_visible + idx_str;
4663
4664 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&dummy_rdc);
4665 (*(cpi->row_mt_sync_read_ptr))(&tile_data->row_mt_sync, sb_row,
4666 sb_col_in_tile);
4667
4668 if (sf->adaptive_pred_interp_filter) {
4669 for (i = 0; i < 64; ++i) td->leaf_tree[i].pred_interp_filter = SWITCHABLE;
4670
4671 for (i = 0; i < 64; ++i) {
4672 td->pc_tree[i].vertical[0].pred_interp_filter = SWITCHABLE;
4673 td->pc_tree[i].vertical[1].pred_interp_filter = SWITCHABLE;
4674 td->pc_tree[i].horizontal[0].pred_interp_filter = SWITCHABLE;
4675 td->pc_tree[i].horizontal[1].pred_interp_filter = SWITCHABLE;
4676 }
4677 }
4678
4679 for (i = 0; i < MAX_REF_FRAMES; ++i) {
4680 x->pred_mv[i].row = INT16_MAX;
4681 x->pred_mv[i].col = INT16_MAX;
4682 }
4683 td->pc_root->index = 0;
4684
4685 if (seg->enabled) {
4686 const uint8_t *const map =
4687 seg->update_map ? cpi->segmentation_map : cm->last_frame_seg_map;
4688 int segment_id = get_segment_id(cm, map, BLOCK_64X64, mi_row, mi_col);
4689 seg_skip = segfeature_active(seg, segment_id, SEG_LVL_SKIP);
4690 }
4691
4692 x->source_variance = UINT_MAX;
4693
4694 x->cb_rdmult = orig_rdmult;
4695
4696 if (sf->partition_search_type == FIXED_PARTITION || seg_skip) {
4697 const BLOCK_SIZE bsize =
4698 seg_skip ? BLOCK_64X64 : sf->always_this_block_size;
4699 set_offsets(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64);
4700 set_fixed_partitioning(cpi, tile_info, mi, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
4701 rd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64,
4702 &dummy_rate, &dummy_dist, 1, td->pc_root);
4703 } else if (cpi->partition_search_skippable_frame) {
4704 BLOCK_SIZE bsize;
4705 set_offsets(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64);
4706 bsize = get_rd_var_based_fixed_partition(cpi, x, mi_row, mi_col);
4707 set_fixed_partitioning(cpi, tile_info, mi, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
4708 rd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64,
4709 &dummy_rate, &dummy_dist, 1, td->pc_root);
4710 } else if (sf->partition_search_type == VAR_BASED_PARTITION &&
4711 cm->frame_type != KEY_FRAME) {
4712 choose_partitioning(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col);
4713 rd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64,
4714 &dummy_rate, &dummy_dist, 1, td->pc_root);
4715 } else {
4716 if (cpi->twopass.gf_group.index > 0 && cpi->sf.enable_tpl_model) {
4717 int dr =
4718 get_rdmult_delta(cpi, BLOCK_64X64, mi_row, mi_col, orig_rdmult);
4719 x->cb_rdmult = dr;
4720 }
4721
4722 if (cpi->oxcf.aq_mode == PERCEPTUAL_AQ && cm->show_frame) {
4723 x->segment_id = wiener_var_segment(cpi, BLOCK_64X64, mi_row, mi_col);
4724 x->cb_rdmult = vp9_compute_rd_mult(
4725 cpi, vp9_get_qindex(&cm->seg, x->segment_id, cm->base_qindex));
4726 }
4727
4728 // If required set upper and lower partition size limits
4729 if (sf->auto_min_max_partition_size) {
4730 set_offsets(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64);
4731 rd_auto_partition_range(cpi, tile_info, xd, mi_row, mi_col,
4732 &x->min_partition_size, &x->max_partition_size);
4733 }
4734 td->pc_root->none.rdcost = 0;
4735 rd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64,
4736 &dummy_rdc, dummy_rdc, td->pc_root);
4737 }
4738 (*(cpi->row_mt_sync_write_ptr))(&tile_data->row_mt_sync, sb_row,
4739 sb_col_in_tile, num_sb_cols);
4740 }
4741}
4742#endif // !CONFIG_REALTIME_ONLY
4743
4744static void init_encode_frame_mb_context(VP9_COMP *cpi) {
4745 MACROBLOCK *const x = &cpi->td.mb;
4746 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
4747 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
4748 const int aligned_mi_cols = mi_cols_aligned_to_sb(cm->mi_cols);
4749
4750 // Copy data over into macro block data structures.
4751 vp9_setup_src_planes(x, cpi->Source, 0, 0);
4752
4753 vp9_setup_block_planes(&x->e_mbd, cm->subsampling_x, cm->subsampling_y);
4754
4755 // Note: this memset assumes above_context[0], [1] and [2]
4756 // are allocated as part of the same buffer.
4757 memset(xd->above_context[0], 0,
4758 sizeof(*xd->above_context[0]) * 2 * aligned_mi_cols * MAX_MB_PLANE);
4759 memset(xd->above_seg_context, 0,
4760 sizeof(*xd->above_seg_context) * aligned_mi_cols);
4761}
4762
4763static int check_dual_ref_flags(VP9_COMP *cpi) {
4764 const int ref_flags = cpi->ref_frame_flags;
4765
4766 if (segfeature_active(&cpi->common.seg, 1, SEG_LVL_REF_FRAME)) {
4767 return 0;
4768 } else {
4769 return (!!(ref_flags & VP9_GOLD_FLAG) + !!(ref_flags & VP9_LAST_FLAG) +
4770 !!(ref_flags & VP9_ALT_FLAG)) >= 2;
4771 }
4772}
4773
4774static void reset_skip_tx_size(VP9_COMMON *cm, TX_SIZE max_tx_size) {
4775 int mi_row, mi_col;
4776 const int mis = cm->mi_stride;
4777 MODE_INFO **mi_ptr = cm->mi_grid_visible;
4778
4779 for (mi_row = 0; mi_row < cm->mi_rows; ++mi_row, mi_ptr += mis) {
4780 for (mi_col = 0; mi_col < cm->mi_cols; ++mi_col) {
4781 if (mi_ptr[mi_col]->tx_size > max_tx_size)
4782 mi_ptr[mi_col]->tx_size = max_tx_size;
4783 }
4784 }
4785}
4786
4787static MV_REFERENCE_FRAME get_frame_type(const VP9_COMP *cpi) {
4788 if (frame_is_intra_only(&cpi->common))
4789 return INTRA_FRAME;
4790 else if (cpi->rc.is_src_frame_alt_ref && cpi->refresh_golden_frame)
4791 return ALTREF_FRAME;
4792 else if (cpi->refresh_golden_frame || cpi->refresh_alt_ref_frame)
4793 return GOLDEN_FRAME;
4794 else
4795 return LAST_FRAME;
4796}
4797
4798static TX_MODE select_tx_mode(const VP9_COMP *cpi, MACROBLOCKD *const xd) {
4799 if (xd->lossless) return ONLY_4X4;
4800 if (cpi->common.frame_type == KEY_FRAME && cpi->sf.use_nonrd_pick_mode)
4801 return ALLOW_16X16;
4802 if (cpi->sf.tx_size_search_method == USE_LARGESTALL)
4803 return ALLOW_32X32;
4804 else if (cpi->sf.tx_size_search_method == USE_FULL_RD ||
4805 cpi->sf.tx_size_search_method == USE_TX_8X8)
4806 return TX_MODE_SELECT;
4807 else
4808 return cpi->common.tx_mode;
4809}
4810
4811static void hybrid_intra_mode_search(VP9_COMP *cpi, MACROBLOCK *const x,
4812 RD_COST *rd_cost, BLOCK_SIZE bsize,
4813 PICK_MODE_CONTEXT *ctx) {
4814 if (!cpi->sf.nonrd_keyframe && bsize < BLOCK_16X16)
4815 vp9_rd_pick_intra_mode_sb(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx, INT64_MAX);
4816 else
4817 vp9_pick_intra_mode(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx);
4818}
4819
4820static void hybrid_search_svc_baseiskey(VP9_COMP *cpi, MACROBLOCK *const x,
4821 RD_COST *rd_cost, BLOCK_SIZE bsize,
4822 PICK_MODE_CONTEXT *ctx,
4823 TileDataEnc *tile_data, int mi_row,
4824 int mi_col) {
4825 if (!cpi->sf.nonrd_keyframe && bsize <= BLOCK_8X8) {
4826 vp9_rd_pick_intra_mode_sb(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx, INT64_MAX);
4827 } else {
4828 if (cpi->svc.disable_inter_layer_pred == INTER_LAYER_PRED_OFF)
4829 vp9_pick_intra_mode(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx);
4830 else if (bsize >= BLOCK_8X8)
4831 vp9_pick_inter_mode(cpi, x, tile_data, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, bsize,
4832 ctx);
4833 else
4834 vp9_pick_inter_mode_sub8x8(cpi, x, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, bsize, ctx);
4835 }
4836}
4837
4838static void hybrid_search_scene_change(VP9_COMP *cpi, MACROBLOCK *const x,
4839 RD_COST *rd_cost, BLOCK_SIZE bsize,
4840 PICK_MODE_CONTEXT *ctx,
4841 TileDataEnc *tile_data, int mi_row,
4842 int mi_col) {
4843 if (!cpi->sf.nonrd_keyframe && bsize <= BLOCK_8X8) {
4844 vp9_rd_pick_intra_mode_sb(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx, INT64_MAX);
4845 } else {
4846 vp9_pick_inter_mode(cpi, x, tile_data, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, bsize, ctx);
4847 }
4848}
4849
4850static void nonrd_pick_sb_modes(VP9_COMP *cpi, TileDataEnc *tile_data,
4851 MACROBLOCK *const x, int mi_row, int mi_col,
4852 RD_COST *rd_cost, BLOCK_SIZE bsize,
4853 PICK_MODE_CONTEXT *ctx) {
4854 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
4855 TileInfo *const tile_info = &tile_data->tile_info;
4856 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
4857 MODE_INFO *mi;
4858 ENTROPY_CONTEXT l[16 * MAX_MB_PLANE], a[16 * MAX_MB_PLANE];
4859 BLOCK_SIZE bs = VPXMAX(bsize, BLOCK_8X8); // processing unit block size
4860 const int num_4x4_blocks_wide = num_4x4_blocks_wide_lookup[bs];
4861 const int num_4x4_blocks_high = num_4x4_blocks_high_lookup[bs];
4862 int plane;
4863
4864 set_offsets(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
4865
4866 set_segment_index(cpi, x, mi_row, mi_col, bsize, 0);
4867
4868 mi = xd->mi[0];
4869 mi->sb_type = bsize;
4870
4871 for (plane = 0; plane < MAX_MB_PLANE; ++plane) {
4872 struct macroblockd_plane *pd = &xd->plane[plane];
4873 memcpy(a + num_4x4_blocks_wide * plane, pd->above_context,
4874 (sizeof(a[0]) * num_4x4_blocks_wide) >> pd->subsampling_x);
4875 memcpy(l + num_4x4_blocks_high * plane, pd->left_context,
4876 (sizeof(l[0]) * num_4x4_blocks_high) >> pd->subsampling_y);
4877 }
4878
4879 if (cpi->oxcf.aq_mode == CYCLIC_REFRESH_AQ && cm->seg.enabled)
4880 if (cyclic_refresh_segment_id_boosted(mi->segment_id))
4881 x->rdmult = vp9_cyclic_refresh_get_rdmult(cpi->cyclic_refresh);
4882
4883 if (frame_is_intra_only(cm))
4884 hybrid_intra_mode_search(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx);
4885 else if (cpi->svc.layer_context[cpi->svc.temporal_layer_id].is_key_frame)
4886 hybrid_search_svc_baseiskey(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx, tile_data, mi_row,
4887 mi_col);
4888 else if (segfeature_active(&cm->seg, mi->segment_id, SEG_LVL_SKIP))
4889 set_mode_info_seg_skip(x, cm->tx_mode, rd_cost, bsize);
4890 else if (bsize >= BLOCK_8X8) {
4891 if (cpi->rc.hybrid_intra_scene_change)
4892 hybrid_search_scene_change(cpi, x, rd_cost, bsize, ctx, tile_data, mi_row,
4893 mi_col);
4894 else
4895 vp9_pick_inter_mode(cpi, x, tile_data, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, bsize,
4896 ctx);
4897 } else {
4898 vp9_pick_inter_mode_sub8x8(cpi, x, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, bsize, ctx);
4899 }
4900
4901 duplicate_mode_info_in_sb(cm, xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
4902
4903 for (plane = 0; plane < MAX_MB_PLANE; ++plane) {
4904 struct macroblockd_plane *pd = &xd->plane[plane];
4905 memcpy(pd->above_context, a + num_4x4_blocks_wide * plane,
4906 (sizeof(a[0]) * num_4x4_blocks_wide) >> pd->subsampling_x);
4907 memcpy(pd->left_context, l + num_4x4_blocks_high * plane,
4908 (sizeof(l[0]) * num_4x4_blocks_high) >> pd->subsampling_y);
4909 }
4910
4911 if (rd_cost->rate == INT_MAX) vp9_rd_cost_reset(rd_cost);
4912
4913 ctx->rate = rd_cost->rate;
4914 ctx->dist = rd_cost->dist;
4915}
4916
4917static void fill_mode_info_sb(VP9_COMMON *cm, MACROBLOCK *x, int mi_row,
4918 int mi_col, BLOCK_SIZE bsize, PC_TREE *pc_tree) {
4919 MACROBLOCKD *xd = &x->e_mbd;
4920 int bsl = b_width_log2_lookup[bsize], hbs = (1 << bsl) / 4;
4921 PARTITION_TYPE partition = pc_tree->partitioning;
4922 BLOCK_SIZE subsize = get_subsize(bsize, partition);
4923
4924 assert(bsize >= BLOCK_8X8);
4925
4926 if (mi_row >= cm->mi_rows || mi_col >= cm->mi_cols) return;
4927
4928 switch (partition) {
4929 case PARTITION_NONE:
4930 set_mode_info_offsets(cm, x, xd, mi_row, mi_col);
4931 *(xd->mi[0]) = pc_tree->none.mic;
4932 *(x->mbmi_ext) = pc_tree->none.mbmi_ext;
4933 duplicate_mode_info_in_sb(cm, xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
4934 break;
4935 case PARTITION_VERT:
4936 set_mode_info_offsets(cm, x, xd, mi_row, mi_col);
4937 *(xd->mi[0]) = pc_tree->vertical[0].mic;
4938 *(x->mbmi_ext) = pc_tree->vertical[0].mbmi_ext;
4939 duplicate_mode_info_in_sb(cm, xd, mi_row, mi_col, subsize);
4940
4941 if (mi_col + hbs < cm->mi_cols) {
4942 set_mode_info_offsets(cm, x, xd, mi_row, mi_col + hbs);
4943 *(xd->mi[0]) = pc_tree->vertical[1].mic;
4944 *(x->mbmi_ext) = pc_tree->vertical[1].mbmi_ext;
4945 duplicate_mode_info_in_sb(cm, xd, mi_row, mi_col + hbs, subsize);
4946 }
4947 break;
4948 case PARTITION_HORZ:
4949 set_mode_info_offsets(cm, x, xd, mi_row, mi_col);
4950 *(xd->mi[0]) = pc_tree->horizontal[0].mic;
4951 *(x->mbmi_ext) = pc_tree->horizontal[0].mbmi_ext;
4952 duplicate_mode_info_in_sb(cm, xd, mi_row, mi_col, subsize);
4953 if (mi_row + hbs < cm->mi_rows) {
4954 set_mode_info_offsets(cm, x, xd, mi_row + hbs, mi_col);
4955 *(xd->mi[0]) = pc_tree->horizontal[1].mic;
4956 *(x->mbmi_ext) = pc_tree->horizontal[1].mbmi_ext;
4957 duplicate_mode_info_in_sb(cm, xd, mi_row + hbs, mi_col, subsize);
4958 }
4959 break;
4960 case PARTITION_SPLIT: {
4961 fill_mode_info_sb(cm, x, mi_row, mi_col, subsize, pc_tree->split[0]);
4962 fill_mode_info_sb(cm, x, mi_row, mi_col + hbs, subsize,
4963 pc_tree->split[1]);
4964 fill_mode_info_sb(cm, x, mi_row + hbs, mi_col, subsize,
4965 pc_tree->split[2]);
4966 fill_mode_info_sb(cm, x, mi_row + hbs, mi_col + hbs, subsize,
4967 pc_tree->split[3]);
4968 break;
4969 }
4970 default: break;
4971 }
4972}
4973
4974// Reset the prediction pixel ready flag recursively.
4975static void pred_pixel_ready_reset(PC_TREE *pc_tree, BLOCK_SIZE bsize) {
4976 pc_tree->none.pred_pixel_ready = 0;
4977 pc_tree->horizontal[0].pred_pixel_ready = 0;
4978 pc_tree->horizontal[1].pred_pixel_ready = 0;
4979 pc_tree->vertical[0].pred_pixel_ready = 0;
4980 pc_tree->vertical[1].pred_pixel_ready = 0;
4981
4982 if (bsize > BLOCK_8X8) {
4983 BLOCK_SIZE subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_SPLIT);
4984 int i;
4985 for (i = 0; i < 4; ++i) pred_pixel_ready_reset(pc_tree->split[i], subsize);
4986 }
4987}
4988
4989#define FEATURES 6
4990#define LABELS 2
4991static int ml_predict_var_paritioning(VP9_COMP *cpi, MACROBLOCK *x,
4992 BLOCK_SIZE bsize, int mi_row,
4993 int mi_col) {
4994 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
4995 const NN_CONFIG *nn_config = NULL;
4996
4997 switch (bsize) {
4998 case BLOCK_64X64: nn_config = &vp9_var_part_nnconfig_64; break;
4999 case BLOCK_32X32: nn_config = &vp9_var_part_nnconfig_32; break;
5000 case BLOCK_16X16: nn_config = &vp9_var_part_nnconfig_16; break;
5001 case BLOCK_8X8: break;
5002 default: assert(0 && "Unexpected block size."); return -1;
5003 }
5004
5005 if (!nn_config) return -1;
5006
5007 vpx_clear_system_state();
5008
5009 {
5010 const float thresh = cpi->oxcf.speed <= 5 ? 1.25f : 0.0f;
5011 float features[FEATURES] = { 0.0f };
5012 const int dc_q = vp9_dc_quant(cm->base_qindex, 0, cm->bit_depth);
5013 int feature_idx = 0;
5014 float score[LABELS];
5015
5016 features[feature_idx++] = logf((float)(dc_q * dc_q) / 256.0f + 1.0f);
5017 vp9_setup_src_planes(x, cpi->Source, mi_row, mi_col);
5018 {
5019 const int bs = 4 * num_4x4_blocks_wide_lookup[bsize];
5020 const BLOCK_SIZE subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_SPLIT);
5021 const int sb_offset_row = 8 * (mi_row & 7);
5022 const int sb_offset_col = 8 * (mi_col & 7);
5023 const uint8_t *pred = x->est_pred + sb_offset_row * 64 + sb_offset_col;
5024 const uint8_t *src = x->plane[0].src.buf;
5025 const int src_stride = x->plane[0].src.stride;
5026 const int pred_stride = 64;
5027 unsigned int sse;
5028 int i;
5029 // Variance of whole block.
5030 const unsigned int var =
5031 cpi->fn_ptr[bsize].vf(src, src_stride, pred, pred_stride, &sse);
5032 const float factor = (var == 0) ? 1.0f : (1.0f / (float)var);
5033
5034 features[feature_idx++] = logf((float)var + 1.0f);
5035 for (i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
5036 const int x_idx = (i & 1) * bs / 2;
5037 const int y_idx = (i >> 1) * bs / 2;
5038 const int src_offset = y_idx * src_stride + x_idx;
5039 const int pred_offset = y_idx * pred_stride + x_idx;
5040 // Variance of quarter block.
5041 const unsigned int sub_var =
5042 cpi->fn_ptr[subsize].vf(src + src_offset, src_stride,
5043 pred + pred_offset, pred_stride, &sse);
5044 const float var_ratio = (var == 0) ? 1.0f : factor * (float)sub_var;
5045 features[feature_idx++] = var_ratio;
5046 }
5047 }
5048
5049 assert(feature_idx == FEATURES);
5050 nn_predict(features, nn_config, score);
5051 if (score[0] > thresh) return PARTITION_SPLIT;
5052 if (score[0] < -thresh) return PARTITION_NONE;
5053 return -1;
5054 }
5055}
5056#undef FEATURES
5057#undef LABELS
5058
5059static void nonrd_pick_partition(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td,
5060 TileDataEnc *tile_data, TOKENEXTRA **tp,
5061 int mi_row, int mi_col, BLOCK_SIZE bsize,
5062 RD_COST *rd_cost, int do_recon,
5063 int64_t best_rd, PC_TREE *pc_tree) {
5064 const SPEED_FEATURES *const sf = &cpi->sf;
5065 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5066 TileInfo *const tile_info = &tile_data->tile_info;
5067 MACROBLOCK *const x = &td->mb;
5068 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
5069 const int ms = num_8x8_blocks_wide_lookup[bsize] / 2;
5070 TOKENEXTRA *tp_orig = *tp;
5071 PICK_MODE_CONTEXT *ctx = &pc_tree->none;
5072 int i;
5073 BLOCK_SIZE subsize = bsize;
5074 RD_COST this_rdc, sum_rdc, best_rdc;
5075 int do_split = bsize >= BLOCK_8X8;
5076 int do_rect = 1;
5077 // Override skipping rectangular partition operations for edge blocks
5078 const int force_horz_split = (mi_row + ms >= cm->mi_rows);
5079 const int force_vert_split = (mi_col + ms >= cm->mi_cols);
5080 const int xss = x->e_mbd.plane[1].subsampling_x;
5081 const int yss = x->e_mbd.plane[1].subsampling_y;
5082
5083 int partition_none_allowed = !force_horz_split && !force_vert_split;
5084 int partition_horz_allowed =
5085 !force_vert_split && yss <= xss && bsize >= BLOCK_8X8;
5086 int partition_vert_allowed =
5087 !force_horz_split && xss <= yss && bsize >= BLOCK_8X8;
5088 const int use_ml_based_partitioning =
5089 sf->partition_search_type == ML_BASED_PARTITION;
5090
5091 (void)*tp_orig;
5092
5093 // Avoid checking for rectangular partitions for speed >= 5.
5094 if (cpi->oxcf.speed >= 5) do_rect = 0;
5095
5096 assert(num_8x8_blocks_wide_lookup[bsize] ==
5097 num_8x8_blocks_high_lookup[bsize]);
5098
5099 vp9_rd_cost_init(&sum_rdc);
5100 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&best_rdc);
5101 best_rdc.rdcost = best_rd;
5102
5103 // Determine partition types in search according to the speed features.
5104 // The threshold set here has to be of square block size.
5105 if (sf->auto_min_max_partition_size) {
5106 partition_none_allowed &=
5107 (bsize <= x->max_partition_size && bsize >= x->min_partition_size);
5108 partition_horz_allowed &=
5109 ((bsize <= x->max_partition_size && bsize > x->min_partition_size) ||
5110 force_horz_split);
5111 partition_vert_allowed &=
5112 ((bsize <= x->max_partition_size && bsize > x->min_partition_size) ||
5113 force_vert_split);
5114 do_split &= bsize > x->min_partition_size;
5115 }
5116 if (sf->use_square_partition_only) {
5117 partition_horz_allowed &= force_horz_split;
5118 partition_vert_allowed &= force_vert_split;
5119 }
5120
5121 if (use_ml_based_partitioning) {
5122 if (partition_none_allowed || do_split) do_rect = 0;
5123 if (partition_none_allowed && do_split) {
5124 const int ml_predicted_partition =
5125 ml_predict_var_paritioning(cpi, x, bsize, mi_row, mi_col);
5126 if (ml_predicted_partition == PARTITION_NONE) do_split = 0;
5127 if (ml_predicted_partition == PARTITION_SPLIT) partition_none_allowed = 0;
5128 }
5129 }
5130
5131 if (!partition_none_allowed && !do_split) do_rect = 1;
5132
5133 ctx->pred_pixel_ready =
5134 !(partition_vert_allowed || partition_horz_allowed || do_split);
5135
5136 // PARTITION_NONE
5137 if (partition_none_allowed) {
5138 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, &this_rdc, bsize,
5139 ctx);
5140 ctx->mic = *xd->mi[0];
5141 ctx->mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5142 ctx->skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5143 ctx->skip = x->skip;
5144
5145 if (this_rdc.rate != INT_MAX) {
5146 const int pl = partition_plane_context(xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
5147 this_rdc.rate += cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_NONE];
5148 this_rdc.rdcost =
5149 RDCOST(x->rdmult, x->rddiv, this_rdc.rate, this_rdc.dist);
5150 if (this_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) {
5151 best_rdc = this_rdc;
5152 if (bsize >= BLOCK_8X8) pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_NONE;
5153
5154 if (!use_ml_based_partitioning) {
5155 int64_t dist_breakout_thr = sf->partition_search_breakout_thr.dist;
5156 int64_t rate_breakout_thr = sf->partition_search_breakout_thr.rate;
5157 dist_breakout_thr >>=
5158 8 - (b_width_log2_lookup[bsize] + b_height_log2_lookup[bsize]);
5159 rate_breakout_thr *= num_pels_log2_lookup[bsize];
5160 if (!x->e_mbd.lossless && this_rdc.rate < rate_breakout_thr &&
5161 this_rdc.dist < dist_breakout_thr) {
5162 do_split = 0;
5163 do_rect = 0;
5164 }
5165 }
5166 }
5167 }
5168 }
5169
5170 // store estimated motion vector
5171 store_pred_mv(x, ctx);
5172
5173 // PARTITION_SPLIT
5174 if (do_split) {
5175 int pl = partition_plane_context(xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
5176 sum_rdc.rate += cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_SPLIT];
5177 sum_rdc.rdcost = RDCOST(x->rdmult, x->rddiv, sum_rdc.rate, sum_rdc.dist);
5178 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_SPLIT);
5179 for (i = 0; i < 4 && sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost; ++i) {
5180 const int x_idx = (i & 1) * ms;
5181 const int y_idx = (i >> 1) * ms;
5182
5183 if (mi_row + y_idx >= cm->mi_rows || mi_col + x_idx >= cm->mi_cols)
5184 continue;
5185 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
5186 nonrd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row + y_idx,
5187 mi_col + x_idx, subsize, &this_rdc, 0,
5188 best_rdc.rdcost - sum_rdc.rdcost, pc_tree->split[i]);
5189
5190 if (this_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
5191 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&sum_rdc);
5192 } else {
5193 sum_rdc.rate += this_rdc.rate;
5194 sum_rdc.dist += this_rdc.dist;
5195 sum_rdc.rdcost += this_rdc.rdcost;
5196 }
5197 }
5198
5199 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) {
5200 best_rdc = sum_rdc;
5201 pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_SPLIT;
5202 } else {
5203 // skip rectangular partition test when larger block size
5204 // gives better rd cost
5205 if (sf->less_rectangular_check) do_rect &= !partition_none_allowed;
5206 }
5207 }
5208
5209 // PARTITION_HORZ
5210 if (partition_horz_allowed && do_rect) {
5211 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_HORZ);
5212 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
5213 pc_tree->horizontal[0].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5214 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, &sum_rdc, subsize,
5215 &pc_tree->horizontal[0]);
5216
5217 pc_tree->horizontal[0].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5218 pc_tree->horizontal[0].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5219 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5220 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip = x->skip;
5221
5222 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost && mi_row + ms < cm->mi_rows) {
5223 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
5224 pc_tree->horizontal[1].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5225 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row + ms, mi_col, &this_rdc,
5226 subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[1]);
5227
5228 pc_tree->horizontal[1].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5229 pc_tree->horizontal[1].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5230 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5231 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip = x->skip;
5232
5233 if (this_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
5234 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&sum_rdc);
5235 } else {
5236 int pl = partition_plane_context(xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
5237 this_rdc.rate += cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_HORZ];
5238 sum_rdc.rate += this_rdc.rate;
5239 sum_rdc.dist += this_rdc.dist;
5240 sum_rdc.rdcost =
5241 RDCOST(x->rdmult, x->rddiv, sum_rdc.rate, sum_rdc.dist);
5242 }
5243 }
5244
5245 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) {
5246 best_rdc = sum_rdc;
5247 pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_HORZ;
5248 } else {
5249 pred_pixel_ready_reset(pc_tree, bsize);
5250 }
5251 }
5252
5253 // PARTITION_VERT
5254 if (partition_vert_allowed && do_rect) {
5255 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_VERT);
5256 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
5257 pc_tree->vertical[0].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5258 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, &sum_rdc, subsize,
5259 &pc_tree->vertical[0]);
5260 pc_tree->vertical[0].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5261 pc_tree->vertical[0].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5262 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5263 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip = x->skip;
5264
5265 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost && mi_col + ms < cm->mi_cols) {
5266 load_pred_mv(x, ctx);
5267 pc_tree->vertical[1].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5268 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col + ms, &this_rdc,
5269 subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[1]);
5270 pc_tree->vertical[1].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5271 pc_tree->vertical[1].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5272 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5273 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip = x->skip;
5274
5275 if (this_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
5276 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&sum_rdc);
5277 } else {
5278 int pl = partition_plane_context(xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
5279 sum_rdc.rate += cpi->partition_cost[pl][PARTITION_VERT];
5280 sum_rdc.rate += this_rdc.rate;
5281 sum_rdc.dist += this_rdc.dist;
5282 sum_rdc.rdcost =
5283 RDCOST(x->rdmult, x->rddiv, sum_rdc.rate, sum_rdc.dist);
5284 }
5285 }
5286
5287 if (sum_rdc.rdcost < best_rdc.rdcost) {
5288 best_rdc = sum_rdc;
5289 pc_tree->partitioning = PARTITION_VERT;
5290 } else {
5291 pred_pixel_ready_reset(pc_tree, bsize);
5292 }
5293 }
5294
5295 *rd_cost = best_rdc;
5296
5297 if (best_rdc.rate == INT_MAX) {
5298 vp9_rd_cost_reset(rd_cost);
5299 return;
5300 }
5301
5302 // update mode info array
5303 fill_mode_info_sb(cm, x, mi_row, mi_col, bsize, pc_tree);
5304
5305 if (best_rdc.rate < INT_MAX && best_rdc.dist < INT64_MAX && do_recon) {
5306 int output_enabled = (bsize == BLOCK_64X64);
5307 encode_sb_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, output_enabled, bsize,
5308 pc_tree);
5309 }
5310
5311 if (bsize == BLOCK_64X64 && do_recon) {
5312 assert(tp_orig < *tp);
5313 assert(best_rdc.rate < INT_MAX);
5314 assert(best_rdc.dist < INT64_MAX);
5315 } else {
5316 assert(tp_orig == *tp);
5317 }
5318}
5319
5320static void nonrd_select_partition(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td,
5321 TileDataEnc *tile_data, MODE_INFO **mi,
5322 TOKENEXTRA **tp, int mi_row, int mi_col,
5323 BLOCK_SIZE bsize, int output_enabled,
5324 RD_COST *rd_cost, PC_TREE *pc_tree) {
5325 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5326 TileInfo *const tile_info = &tile_data->tile_info;
5327 MACROBLOCK *const x = &td->mb;
5328 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
5329 const int bsl = b_width_log2_lookup[bsize], hbs = (1 << bsl) / 4;
5330 const int mis = cm->mi_stride;
5331 PARTITION_TYPE partition;
5332 BLOCK_SIZE subsize;
5333 RD_COST this_rdc;
5334 BLOCK_SIZE subsize_ref =
5335 (cpi->sf.adapt_partition_source_sad) ? BLOCK_8X8 : BLOCK_16X16;
5336
5337 vp9_rd_cost_reset(&this_rdc);
5338 if (mi_row >= cm->mi_rows || mi_col >= cm->mi_cols) return;
5339
5340 subsize = (bsize >= BLOCK_8X8) ? mi[0]->sb_type : BLOCK_4X4;
5341 partition = partition_lookup[bsl][subsize];
5342
5343 if (bsize == BLOCK_32X32 && subsize == BLOCK_32X32) {
5344 x->max_partition_size = BLOCK_32X32;
5345 x->min_partition_size = BLOCK_16X16;
5346 nonrd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row, mi_col, bsize, rd_cost,
5347 0, INT64_MAX, pc_tree);
5348 } else if (bsize == BLOCK_32X32 && partition != PARTITION_NONE &&
5349 subsize >= subsize_ref) {
5350 x->max_partition_size = BLOCK_32X32;
5351 x->min_partition_size = BLOCK_8X8;
5352 nonrd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row, mi_col, bsize, rd_cost,
5353 0, INT64_MAX, pc_tree);
5354 } else if (bsize == BLOCK_16X16 && partition != PARTITION_NONE) {
5355 x->max_partition_size = BLOCK_16X16;
5356 x->min_partition_size = BLOCK_8X8;
5357 nonrd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row, mi_col, bsize, rd_cost,
5358 0, INT64_MAX, pc_tree);
5359 } else {
5360 switch (partition) {
5361 case PARTITION_NONE:
5362 pc_tree->none.pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5363 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, subsize,
5364 &pc_tree->none);
5365 pc_tree->none.mic = *xd->mi[0];
5366 pc_tree->none.mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5367 pc_tree->none.skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5368 pc_tree->none.skip = x->skip;
5369 break;
5370 case PARTITION_VERT:
5371 pc_tree->vertical[0].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5372 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, subsize,
5373 &pc_tree->vertical[0]);
5374 pc_tree->vertical[0].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5375 pc_tree->vertical[0].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5376 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5377 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip = x->skip;
5378 if (mi_col + hbs < cm->mi_cols) {
5379 pc_tree->vertical[1].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5380 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col + hbs,
5381 &this_rdc, subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[1]);
5382 pc_tree->vertical[1].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5383 pc_tree->vertical[1].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5384 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5385 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip = x->skip;
5386 if (this_rdc.rate != INT_MAX && this_rdc.dist != INT64_MAX &&
5387 rd_cost->rate != INT_MAX && rd_cost->dist != INT64_MAX) {
5388 rd_cost->rate += this_rdc.rate;
5389 rd_cost->dist += this_rdc.dist;
5390 }
5391 }
5392 break;
5393 case PARTITION_HORZ:
5394 pc_tree->horizontal[0].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5395 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, rd_cost, subsize,
5396 &pc_tree->horizontal[0]);
5397 pc_tree->horizontal[0].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5398 pc_tree->horizontal[0].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5399 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5400 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip = x->skip;
5401 if (mi_row + hbs < cm->mi_rows) {
5402 pc_tree->horizontal[1].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5403 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row + hbs, mi_col,
5404 &this_rdc, subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[1]);
5405 pc_tree->horizontal[1].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5406 pc_tree->horizontal[1].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5407 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5408 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip = x->skip;
5409 if (this_rdc.rate != INT_MAX && this_rdc.dist != INT64_MAX &&
5410 rd_cost->rate != INT_MAX && rd_cost->dist != INT64_MAX) {
5411 rd_cost->rate += this_rdc.rate;
5412 rd_cost->dist += this_rdc.dist;
5413 }
5414 }
5415 break;
5416 default:
5417 assert(partition == PARTITION_SPLIT);
5418 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_SPLIT);
5419 nonrd_select_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5420 subsize, output_enabled, rd_cost,
5421 pc_tree->split[0]);
5422 nonrd_select_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi + hbs, tp, mi_row,
5423 mi_col + hbs, subsize, output_enabled, &this_rdc,
5424 pc_tree->split[1]);
5425 if (this_rdc.rate != INT_MAX && this_rdc.dist != INT64_MAX &&
5426 rd_cost->rate != INT_MAX && rd_cost->dist != INT64_MAX) {
5427 rd_cost->rate += this_rdc.rate;
5428 rd_cost->dist += this_rdc.dist;
5429 }
5430 nonrd_select_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi + hbs * mis, tp,
5431 mi_row + hbs, mi_col, subsize, output_enabled,
5432 &this_rdc, pc_tree->split[2]);
5433 if (this_rdc.rate != INT_MAX && this_rdc.dist != INT64_MAX &&
5434 rd_cost->rate != INT_MAX && rd_cost->dist != INT64_MAX) {
5435 rd_cost->rate += this_rdc.rate;
5436 rd_cost->dist += this_rdc.dist;
5437 }
5438 nonrd_select_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi + hbs * mis + hbs, tp,
5439 mi_row + hbs, mi_col + hbs, subsize,
5440 output_enabled, &this_rdc, pc_tree->split[3]);
5441 if (this_rdc.rate != INT_MAX && this_rdc.dist != INT64_MAX &&
5442 rd_cost->rate != INT_MAX && rd_cost->dist != INT64_MAX) {
5443 rd_cost->rate += this_rdc.rate;
5444 rd_cost->dist += this_rdc.dist;
5445 }
5446 break;
5447 }
5448 }
5449
5450 if (bsize == BLOCK_64X64 && output_enabled)
5451 encode_sb_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, 1, bsize, pc_tree);
5452}
5453
5454static void nonrd_use_partition(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td,
5455 TileDataEnc *tile_data, MODE_INFO **mi,
5456 TOKENEXTRA **tp, int mi_row, int mi_col,
5457 BLOCK_SIZE bsize, int output_enabled,
5458 RD_COST *dummy_cost, PC_TREE *pc_tree) {
5459 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5460 TileInfo *tile_info = &tile_data->tile_info;
5461 MACROBLOCK *const x = &td->mb;
5462 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
5463 const int bsl = b_width_log2_lookup[bsize], hbs = (1 << bsl) / 4;
5464 const int mis = cm->mi_stride;
5465 PARTITION_TYPE partition;
5466 BLOCK_SIZE subsize;
5467
5468 if (mi_row >= cm->mi_rows || mi_col >= cm->mi_cols) return;
5469
5470 subsize = (bsize >= BLOCK_8X8) ? mi[0]->sb_type : BLOCK_4X4;
5471 partition = partition_lookup[bsl][subsize];
5472
5473 if (output_enabled && bsize != BLOCK_4X4) {
5474 int ctx = partition_plane_context(xd, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
5475 td->counts->partition[ctx][partition]++;
5476 }
5477
5478 switch (partition) {
5479 case PARTITION_NONE:
5480 pc_tree->none.pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5481 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, dummy_cost,
5482 subsize, &pc_tree->none);
5483 pc_tree->none.mic = *xd->mi[0];
5484 pc_tree->none.mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5485 pc_tree->none.skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5486 pc_tree->none.skip = x->skip;
5487 encode_b_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, output_enabled,
5488 subsize, &pc_tree->none);
5489 break;
5490 case PARTITION_VERT:
5491 pc_tree->vertical[0].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5492 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, dummy_cost,
5493 subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[0]);
5494 pc_tree->vertical[0].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5495 pc_tree->vertical[0].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5496 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5497 pc_tree->vertical[0].skip = x->skip;
5498 encode_b_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, output_enabled,
5499 subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[0]);
5500 if (mi_col + hbs < cm->mi_cols && bsize > BLOCK_8X8) {
5501 pc_tree->vertical[1].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5502 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col + hbs, dummy_cost,
5503 subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[1]);
5504 pc_tree->vertical[1].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5505 pc_tree->vertical[1].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5506 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5507 pc_tree->vertical[1].skip = x->skip;
5508 encode_b_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col + hbs,
5509 output_enabled, subsize, &pc_tree->vertical[1]);
5510 }
5511 break;
5512 case PARTITION_HORZ:
5513 pc_tree->horizontal[0].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5514 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, dummy_cost,
5515 subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[0]);
5516 pc_tree->horizontal[0].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5517 pc_tree->horizontal[0].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5518 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5519 pc_tree->horizontal[0].skip = x->skip;
5520 encode_b_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, output_enabled,
5521 subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[0]);
5522
5523 if (mi_row + hbs < cm->mi_rows && bsize > BLOCK_8X8) {
5524 pc_tree->horizontal[1].pred_pixel_ready = 1;
5525 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row + hbs, mi_col, dummy_cost,
5526 subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[1]);
5527 pc_tree->horizontal[1].mic = *xd->mi[0];
5528 pc_tree->horizontal[1].mbmi_ext = *x->mbmi_ext;
5529 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip_txfm[0] = x->skip_txfm[0];
5530 pc_tree->horizontal[1].skip = x->skip;
5531 encode_b_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row + hbs, mi_col,
5532 output_enabled, subsize, &pc_tree->horizontal[1]);
5533 }
5534 break;
5535 default:
5536 assert(partition == PARTITION_SPLIT);
5537 subsize = get_subsize(bsize, PARTITION_SPLIT);
5538 if (bsize == BLOCK_8X8) {
5539 nonrd_pick_sb_modes(cpi, tile_data, x, mi_row, mi_col, dummy_cost,
5540 subsize, pc_tree->leaf_split[0]);
5541 encode_b_rt(cpi, td, tile_info, tp, mi_row, mi_col, output_enabled,
5542 subsize, pc_tree->leaf_split[0]);
5543 } else {
5544 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col, subsize,
5545 output_enabled, dummy_cost, pc_tree->split[0]);
5546 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi + hbs, tp, mi_row,
5547 mi_col + hbs, subsize, output_enabled, dummy_cost,
5548 pc_tree->split[1]);
5549 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi + hbs * mis, tp,
5550 mi_row + hbs, mi_col, subsize, output_enabled,
5551 dummy_cost, pc_tree->split[2]);
5552 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi + hbs * mis + hbs, tp,
5553 mi_row + hbs, mi_col + hbs, subsize, output_enabled,
5554 dummy_cost, pc_tree->split[3]);
5555 }
5556 break;
5557 }
5558
5559 if (partition != PARTITION_SPLIT || bsize == BLOCK_8X8)
5560 update_partition_context(xd, mi_row, mi_col, subsize, bsize);
5561}
5562
5563// Get a prediction(stored in x->est_pred) for the whole 64x64 superblock.
5564static void get_estimated_pred(VP9_COMP *cpi, const TileInfo *const tile,
5565 MACROBLOCK *x, int mi_row, int mi_col) {
5566 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5567 const int is_key_frame = frame_is_intra_only(cm);
5568 MACROBLOCKD *xd = &x->e_mbd;
5569
5570 set_offsets(cpi, tile, x, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64);
5571
5572 if (!is_key_frame) {
5573 MODE_INFO *mi = xd->mi[0];
5574 YV12_BUFFER_CONFIG *yv12 = get_ref_frame_buffer(cpi, LAST_FRAME);
5575 const YV12_BUFFER_CONFIG *yv12_g = NULL;
5576 const BLOCK_SIZE bsize = BLOCK_32X32 + (mi_col + 4 < cm->mi_cols) * 2 +
5577 (mi_row + 4 < cm->mi_rows);
5578 unsigned int y_sad_g, y_sad_thr;
5579 unsigned int y_sad = UINT_MAX;
5580
5581 assert(yv12 != NULL);
5582
5583 if (!(is_one_pass_cbr_svc(cpi) && cpi->svc.spatial_layer_id) ||
5584 cpi->svc.use_gf_temporal_ref_current_layer) {
5585 // For now, GOLDEN will not be used for non-zero spatial layers, since
5586 // it may not be a temporal reference.
5587 yv12_g = get_ref_frame_buffer(cpi, GOLDEN_FRAME);
5588 }
5589
5590 // Only compute y_sad_g (sad for golden reference) for speed < 8.
5591 if (cpi->oxcf.speed < 8 && yv12_g && yv12_g != yv12 &&
5592 (cpi->ref_frame_flags & VP9_GOLD_FLAG)) {
5593 vp9_setup_pre_planes(xd, 0, yv12_g, mi_row, mi_col,
5594 &cm->frame_refs[GOLDEN_FRAME - 1].sf);
5595 y_sad_g = cpi->fn_ptr[bsize].sdf(
5596 x->plane[0].src.buf, x->plane[0].src.stride, xd->plane[0].pre[0].buf,
5597 xd->plane[0].pre[0].stride);
5598 } else {
5599 y_sad_g = UINT_MAX;
5600 }
5601
5602 if (cpi->oxcf.lag_in_frames > 0 && cpi->oxcf.rc_mode == VPX_VBR &&
5603 cpi->rc.is_src_frame_alt_ref) {
5604 yv12 = get_ref_frame_buffer(cpi, ALTREF_FRAME);
5605 vp9_setup_pre_planes(xd, 0, yv12, mi_row, mi_col,
5606 &cm->frame_refs[ALTREF_FRAME - 1].sf);
5607 mi->ref_frame[0] = ALTREF_FRAME;
5608 y_sad_g = UINT_MAX;
5609 } else {
5610 vp9_setup_pre_planes(xd, 0, yv12, mi_row, mi_col,
5611 &cm->frame_refs[LAST_FRAME - 1].sf);
5612 mi->ref_frame[0] = LAST_FRAME;
5613 }
5614 mi->ref_frame[1] = NONE;
5615 mi->sb_type = BLOCK_64X64;
5616 mi->mv[0].as_int = 0;
5617 mi->interp_filter = BILINEAR;
5618
5619 {
5620 const MV dummy_mv = { 0, 0 };
5621 y_sad = vp9_int_pro_motion_estimation(cpi, x, bsize, mi_row, mi_col,
5622 &dummy_mv);
5623 x->sb_use_mv_part = 1;
5624 x->sb_mvcol_part = mi->mv[0].as_mv.col;
5625 x->sb_mvrow_part = mi->mv[0].as_mv.row;
5626 }
5627
5628 // Pick ref frame for partitioning, bias last frame when y_sad_g and y_sad
5629 // are close if short_circuit_low_temp_var is on.
5630 y_sad_thr = cpi->sf.short_circuit_low_temp_var ? (y_sad * 7) >> 3 : y_sad;
5631 if (y_sad_g < y_sad_thr) {
5632 vp9_setup_pre_planes(xd, 0, yv12_g, mi_row, mi_col,
5633 &cm->frame_refs[GOLDEN_FRAME - 1].sf);
5634 mi->ref_frame[0] = GOLDEN_FRAME;
5635 mi->mv[0].as_int = 0;
5636 } else {
5637 x->pred_mv[LAST_FRAME] = mi->mv[0].as_mv;
5638 }
5639
5640 set_ref_ptrs(cm, xd, mi->ref_frame[0], mi->ref_frame[1]);
5641 xd->plane[0].dst.buf = x->est_pred;
5642 xd->plane[0].dst.stride = 64;
5643 vp9_build_inter_predictors_sb(xd, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64);
5644 } else {
5645#if CONFIG_VP9_HIGHBITDEPTH
5646 switch (xd->bd) {
5647 case 8: memset(x->est_pred, 128, 64 * 64 * sizeof(x->est_pred[0])); break;
5648 case 10:
5649 memset(x->est_pred, 128 * 4, 64 * 64 * sizeof(x->est_pred[0]));
5650 break;
5651 case 12:
5652 memset(x->est_pred, 128 * 16, 64 * 64 * sizeof(x->est_pred[0]));
5653 break;
5654 }
5655#else
5656 memset(x->est_pred, 128, 64 * 64 * sizeof(x->est_pred[0]));
5657#endif // CONFIG_VP9_HIGHBITDEPTH
5658 }
5659}
5660
5661static void encode_nonrd_sb_row(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td,
5662 TileDataEnc *tile_data, int mi_row,
5663 TOKENEXTRA **tp) {
5664 SPEED_FEATURES *const sf = &cpi->sf;
5665 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5666 TileInfo *const tile_info = &tile_data->tile_info;
5667 MACROBLOCK *const x = &td->mb;
5668 MACROBLOCKD *const xd = &x->e_mbd;
5669 const int mi_col_start = tile_info->mi_col_start;
5670 const int mi_col_end = tile_info->mi_col_end;
5671 int mi_col;
5672 const int sb_row = mi_row >> MI_BLOCK_SIZE_LOG2;
5673 const int num_sb_cols =
5674 get_num_cols(tile_data->tile_info, MI_BLOCK_SIZE_LOG2);
5675 int sb_col_in_tile;
5676
5677 // Initialize the left context for the new SB row
5678 memset(&xd->left_context, 0, sizeof(xd->left_context));
5679 memset(xd->left_seg_context, 0, sizeof(xd->left_seg_context));
5680
5681 // Code each SB in the row
5682 for (mi_col = mi_col_start, sb_col_in_tile = 0; mi_col < mi_col_end;
5683 mi_col += MI_BLOCK_SIZE, ++sb_col_in_tile) {
5684 const struct segmentation *const seg = &cm->seg;
5685 RD_COST dummy_rdc;
5686 const int idx_str = cm->mi_stride * mi_row + mi_col;
5687 MODE_INFO **mi = cm->mi_grid_visible + idx_str;
5688 PARTITION_SEARCH_TYPE partition_search_type = sf->partition_search_type;
5689 BLOCK_SIZE bsize = BLOCK_64X64;
5690 int seg_skip = 0;
5691 int i;
5692
5693 (*(cpi->row_mt_sync_read_ptr))(&tile_data->row_mt_sync, sb_row,
5694 sb_col_in_tile);
5695
5696 if (cpi->use_skin_detection) {
5697 vp9_compute_skin_sb(cpi, BLOCK_16X16, mi_row, mi_col);
5698 }
5699
5700 x->source_variance = UINT_MAX;
5701 for (i = 0; i < MAX_REF_FRAMES; ++i) {
5702 x->pred_mv[i].row = INT16_MAX;
5703 x->pred_mv[i].col = INT16_MAX;
5704 }
5705 vp9_rd_cost_init(&dummy_rdc);
5706 x->color_sensitivity[0] = 0;
5707 x->color_sensitivity[1] = 0;
5708 x->sb_is_skin = 0;
5709 x->skip_low_source_sad = 0;
5710 x->lowvar_highsumdiff = 0;
5711 x->content_state_sb = 0;
5712 x->zero_temp_sad_source = 0;
5713 x->sb_use_mv_part = 0;
5714 x->sb_mvcol_part = 0;
5715 x->sb_mvrow_part = 0;
5716 x->sb_pickmode_part = 0;
5717 x->arf_frame_usage = 0;
5718 x->lastgolden_frame_usage = 0;
5719
5720 if (seg->enabled) {
5721 const uint8_t *const map =
5722 seg->update_map ? cpi->segmentation_map : cm->last_frame_seg_map;
5723 int segment_id = get_segment_id(cm, map, BLOCK_64X64, mi_row, mi_col);
5724 seg_skip = segfeature_active(seg, segment_id, SEG_LVL_SKIP);
5725 if (seg_skip) {
5726 partition_search_type = FIXED_PARTITION;
5727 }
5728 }
5729
5730 if (cpi->compute_source_sad_onepass && cpi->sf.use_source_sad) {
5731 int shift = cpi->Source->y_stride * (mi_row << 3) + (mi_col << 3);
5732 int sb_offset2 = ((cm->mi_cols + 7) >> 3) * (mi_row >> 3) + (mi_col >> 3);
5733 int64_t source_sad = avg_source_sad(cpi, x, shift, sb_offset2);
5734 if (sf->adapt_partition_source_sad &&
5735 (cpi->oxcf.rc_mode == VPX_VBR && !cpi->rc.is_src_frame_alt_ref &&
5736 source_sad > sf->adapt_partition_thresh &&
5737 (cpi->refresh_golden_frame || cpi->refresh_alt_ref_frame)))
5738 partition_search_type = REFERENCE_PARTITION;
5739 }
5740
5741 // Set the partition type of the 64X64 block
5742 switch (partition_search_type) {
5743 case VAR_BASED_PARTITION:
5744 // TODO(jingning, marpan): The mode decision and encoding process
5745 // support both intra and inter sub8x8 block coding for RTC mode.
5746 // Tune the thresholds accordingly to use sub8x8 block coding for
5747 // coding performance improvement.
5748 choose_partitioning(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col);
5749 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5750 BLOCK_64X64, 1, &dummy_rdc, td->pc_root);
5751 break;
5752 case ML_BASED_PARTITION:
5753 get_estimated_pred(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col);
5754 x->max_partition_size = BLOCK_64X64;
5755 x->min_partition_size = BLOCK_8X8;
5756 x->sb_pickmode_part = 1;
5757 nonrd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5758 BLOCK_64X64, &dummy_rdc, 1, INT64_MAX,
5759 td->pc_root);
5760 break;
5761 case SOURCE_VAR_BASED_PARTITION:
5762 set_source_var_based_partition(cpi, tile_info, x, mi, mi_row, mi_col);
5763 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5764 BLOCK_64X64, 1, &dummy_rdc, td->pc_root);
5765 break;
5766 case FIXED_PARTITION:
5767 if (!seg_skip) bsize = sf->always_this_block_size;
5768 set_fixed_partitioning(cpi, tile_info, mi, mi_row, mi_col, bsize);
5769 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5770 BLOCK_64X64, 1, &dummy_rdc, td->pc_root);
5771 break;
5772 default:
5773 assert(partition_search_type == REFERENCE_PARTITION);
5774 x->sb_pickmode_part = 1;
5775 set_offsets(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col, BLOCK_64X64);
5776 // Use nonrd_pick_partition on scene-cut for VBR mode.
5777 // nonrd_pick_partition does not support 4x4 partition, so avoid it
5778 // on key frame for now.
5779 if ((cpi->oxcf.rc_mode == VPX_VBR && cpi->rc.high_source_sad &&
5780 cpi->oxcf.speed < 6 && !frame_is_intra_only(cm) &&
5781 (cpi->refresh_golden_frame || cpi->refresh_alt_ref_frame))) {
5782 // Use lower max_partition_size for low resoultions.
5783 if (cm->width <= 352 && cm->height <= 288)
5784 x->max_partition_size = BLOCK_32X32;
5785 else
5786 x->max_partition_size = BLOCK_64X64;
5787 x->min_partition_size = BLOCK_8X8;
5788 nonrd_pick_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5789 BLOCK_64X64, &dummy_rdc, 1, INT64_MAX,
5790 td->pc_root);
5791 } else {
5792 choose_partitioning(cpi, tile_info, x, mi_row, mi_col);
5793 // TODO(marpan): Seems like nonrd_select_partition does not support
5794 // 4x4 partition. Since 4x4 is used on key frame, use this switch
5795 // for now.
5796 if (frame_is_intra_only(cm))
5797 nonrd_use_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5798 BLOCK_64X64, 1, &dummy_rdc, td->pc_root);
5799 else
5800 nonrd_select_partition(cpi, td, tile_data, mi, tp, mi_row, mi_col,
5801 BLOCK_64X64, 1, &dummy_rdc, td->pc_root);
5802 }
5803
5804 break;
5805 }
5806
5807 // Update ref_frame usage for inter frame if this group is ARF group.
5808 if (!cpi->rc.is_src_frame_alt_ref && !cpi->refresh_golden_frame &&
5809 !cpi->refresh_alt_ref_frame && cpi->rc.alt_ref_gf_group &&
5810 cpi->sf.use_altref_onepass) {
5811 int sboffset = ((cm->mi_cols + 7) >> 3) * (mi_row >> 3) + (mi_col >> 3);
5812 if (cpi->count_arf_frame_usage != NULL)
5813 cpi->count_arf_frame_usage[sboffset] = x->arf_frame_usage;
5814 if (cpi->count_lastgolden_frame_usage != NULL)
5815 cpi->count_lastgolden_frame_usage[sboffset] = x->lastgolden_frame_usage;
5816 }
5817
5818 (*(cpi->row_mt_sync_write_ptr))(&tile_data->row_mt_sync, sb_row,
5819 sb_col_in_tile, num_sb_cols);
5820 }
5821}
5822// end RTC play code
5823
5824static INLINE uint32_t variance(const diff *const d) {
5825 return d->sse - (uint32_t)(((int64_t)d->sum * d->sum) >> 8);
5826}
5827
5828#if CONFIG_VP9_HIGHBITDEPTH
5829static INLINE uint32_t variance_highbd(diff *const d) {
5830 const int64_t var = (int64_t)d->sse - (((int64_t)d->sum * d->sum) >> 8);
5831 return (var >= 0) ? (uint32_t)var : 0;
5832}
5833#endif // CONFIG_VP9_HIGHBITDEPTH
5834
5835static int set_var_thresh_from_histogram(VP9_COMP *cpi) {
5836 const SPEED_FEATURES *const sf = &cpi->sf;
5837 const VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5838
5839 const uint8_t *src = cpi->Source->y_buffer;
5840 const uint8_t *last_src = cpi->Last_Source->y_buffer;
5841 const int src_stride = cpi->Source->y_stride;
5842 const int last_stride = cpi->Last_Source->y_stride;
5843
5844 // Pick cutoff threshold
5845 const int cutoff = (VPXMIN(cm->width, cm->height) >= 720)
5846 ? (cm->MBs * VAR_HIST_LARGE_CUT_OFF / 100)
5847 : (cm->MBs * VAR_HIST_SMALL_CUT_OFF / 100);
5848 DECLARE_ALIGNED(16, int, hist[VAR_HIST_BINS]);
5849 diff *var16 = cpi->source_diff_var;
5850
5851 int sum = 0;
5852 int i, j;
5853
5854 memset(hist, 0, VAR_HIST_BINS * sizeof(hist[0]));
5855
5856 for (i = 0; i < cm->mb_rows; i++) {
5857 for (j = 0; j < cm->mb_cols; j++) {
5858#if CONFIG_VP9_HIGHBITDEPTH
5859 if (cm->use_highbitdepth) {
5860 switch (cm->bit_depth) {
5861 case VPX_BITS_8:
5862 vpx_highbd_8_get16x16var(src, src_stride, last_src, last_stride,
5863 &var16->sse, &var16->sum);
5864 var16->var = variance(var16);
5865 break;
5866 case VPX_BITS_10:
5867 vpx_highbd_10_get16x16var(src, src_stride, last_src, last_stride,
5868 &var16->sse, &var16->sum);
5869 var16->var = variance_highbd(var16);
5870 break;
5871 default:
5872 assert(cm->bit_depth == VPX_BITS_12);
5873 vpx_highbd_12_get16x16var(src, src_stride, last_src, last_stride,
5874 &var16->sse, &var16->sum);
5875 var16->var = variance_highbd(var16);
5876 break;
5877 }
5878 } else {
5879 vpx_get16x16var(src, src_stride, last_src, last_stride, &var16->sse,
5880 &var16->sum);
5881 var16->var = variance(var16);
5882 }
5883#else
5884 vpx_get16x16var(src, src_stride, last_src, last_stride, &var16->sse,
5885 &var16->sum);
5886 var16->var = variance(var16);
5887#endif // CONFIG_VP9_HIGHBITDEPTH
5888
5889 if (var16->var >= VAR_HIST_MAX_BG_VAR)
5890 hist[VAR_HIST_BINS - 1]++;
5891 else
5892 hist[var16->var / VAR_HIST_FACTOR]++;
5893
5894 src += 16;
5895 last_src += 16;
5896 var16++;
5897 }
5898
5899 src = src - cm->mb_cols * 16 + 16 * src_stride;
5900 last_src = last_src - cm->mb_cols * 16 + 16 * last_stride;
5901 }
5902
5903 cpi->source_var_thresh = 0;
5904
5905 if (hist[VAR_HIST_BINS - 1] < cutoff) {
5906 for (i = 0; i < VAR_HIST_BINS - 1; i++) {
5907 sum += hist[i];
5908
5909 if (sum > cutoff) {
5910 cpi->source_var_thresh = (i + 1) * VAR_HIST_FACTOR;
5911 return 0;
5912 }
5913 }
5914 }
5915
5916 return sf->search_type_check_frequency;
5917}
5918
5919static void source_var_based_partition_search_method(VP9_COMP *cpi) {
5920 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5921 SPEED_FEATURES *const sf = &cpi->sf;
5922
5923 if (cm->frame_type == KEY_FRAME) {
5924 // For key frame, use SEARCH_PARTITION.
5925 sf->partition_search_type = SEARCH_PARTITION;
5926 } else if (cm->intra_only) {
5927 sf->partition_search_type = FIXED_PARTITION;
5928 } else {
5929 if (cm->last_width != cm->width || cm->last_height != cm->height) {
5930 if (cpi->source_diff_var) vpx_free(cpi->source_diff_var);
5931
5932 CHECK_MEM_ERROR(cm, cpi->source_diff_var,
5933 vpx_calloc(cm->MBs, sizeof(diff)));
5934 }
5935
5936 if (!cpi->frames_till_next_var_check)
5937 cpi->frames_till_next_var_check = set_var_thresh_from_histogram(cpi);
5938
5939 if (cpi->frames_till_next_var_check > 0) {
5940 sf->partition_search_type = FIXED_PARTITION;
5941 cpi->frames_till_next_var_check--;
5942 }
5943 }
5944}
5945
5946static int get_skip_encode_frame(const VP9_COMMON *cm, ThreadData *const td) {
5947 unsigned int intra_count = 0, inter_count = 0;
5948 int j;
5949
5950 for (j = 0; j < INTRA_INTER_CONTEXTS; ++j) {
5951 intra_count += td->counts->intra_inter[j][0];
5952 inter_count += td->counts->intra_inter[j][1];
5953 }
5954
5955 return (intra_count << 2) < inter_count && cm->frame_type != KEY_FRAME &&
5956 cm->show_frame;
5957}
5958
5959void vp9_init_tile_data(VP9_COMP *cpi) {
5960 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
5961 const int tile_cols = 1 << cm->log2_tile_cols;
5962 const int tile_rows = 1 << cm->log2_tile_rows;
5963 int tile_col, tile_row;
5964 TOKENEXTRA *pre_tok = cpi->tile_tok[0][0];
5965 TOKENLIST *tplist = cpi->tplist[0][0];
5966 int tile_tok = 0;
5967 int tplist_count = 0;
5968
5969 if (cpi->tile_data == NULL || cpi->allocated_tiles < tile_cols * tile_rows) {
5970 if (cpi->tile_data != NULL) vpx_free(cpi->tile_data);
5971 CHECK_MEM_ERROR(
5972 cm, cpi->tile_data,
5973 vpx_malloc(tile_cols * tile_rows * sizeof(*cpi->tile_data)));
5974 cpi->allocated_tiles = tile_cols * tile_rows;
5975
5976 for (tile_row = 0; tile_row < tile_rows; ++tile_row)
5977 for (tile_col = 0; tile_col < tile_cols; ++tile_col) {
5978 TileDataEnc *tile_data =
5979 &cpi->tile_data[tile_row * tile_cols + tile_col];
5980 int i, j;
5981 for (i = 0; i < BLOCK_SIZES; ++i) {
5982 for (j = 0; j < MAX_MODES; ++j) {
5983 tile_data->thresh_freq_fact[i][j] = RD_THRESH_INIT_FACT;
5984#if CONFIG_CONSISTENT_RECODE || CONFIG_RATE_CTRL
5985 tile_data->thresh_freq_fact_prev[i][j] = RD_THRESH_INIT_FACT;
5986#endif // CONFIG_CONSISTENT_RECODE || CONFIG_RATE_CTRL
5987 tile_data->mode_map[i][j] = j;
5988 }
5989 }
5990#if CONFIG_MULTITHREAD
5991 tile_data->row_base_thresh_freq_fact = NULL;
5992#endif
5993 }
5994 }
5995
5996 for (tile_row = 0; tile_row < tile_rows; ++tile_row) {
5997 for (tile_col = 0; tile_col < tile_cols; ++tile_col) {
5998 TileDataEnc *this_tile = &cpi->tile_data[tile_row * tile_cols + tile_col];
5999 TileInfo *tile_info = &this_tile->tile_info;
6000 if (cpi->sf.adaptive_rd_thresh_row_mt &&
6001 this_tile->row_base_thresh_freq_fact == NULL)
6002 vp9_row_mt_alloc_rd_thresh(cpi, this_tile);
6003 vp9_tile_init(tile_info, cm, tile_row, tile_col);
6004
6005 cpi->tile_tok[tile_row][tile_col] = pre_tok + tile_tok;
6006 pre_tok = cpi->tile_tok[tile_row][tile_col];
6007 tile_tok = allocated_tokens(*tile_info);
6008
6009 cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col] = tplist + tplist_count;
6010 tplist = cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col];
6011 tplist_count = get_num_vert_units(*tile_info, MI_BLOCK_SIZE_LOG2);
6012 }
6013 }
6014}
6015
6016void vp9_encode_sb_row(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td, int tile_row,
6017 int tile_col, int mi_row) {
6018 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
6019 const int tile_cols = 1 << cm->log2_tile_cols;
6020 TileDataEnc *this_tile = &cpi->tile_data[tile_row * tile_cols + tile_col];
6021 const TileInfo *const tile_info = &this_tile->tile_info;
6022 TOKENEXTRA *tok = NULL;
6023 int tile_sb_row;
6024 int tile_mb_cols = (tile_info->mi_col_end - tile_info->mi_col_start + 1) >> 1;
6025
6026 tile_sb_row = mi_cols_aligned_to_sb(mi_row - tile_info->mi_row_start) >>
6027 MI_BLOCK_SIZE_LOG2;
6028 get_start_tok(cpi, tile_row, tile_col, mi_row, &tok);
6029 cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col][tile_sb_row].start = tok;
6030
6031 if (cpi->sf.use_nonrd_pick_mode)
6032 encode_nonrd_sb_row(cpi, td, this_tile, mi_row, &tok);
6033#if !CONFIG_REALTIME_ONLY
6034 else
6035 encode_rd_sb_row(cpi, td, this_tile, mi_row, &tok);
6036#endif
6037
6038 cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col][tile_sb_row].stop = tok;
6039 cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col][tile_sb_row].count =
6040 (unsigned int)(cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col][tile_sb_row].stop -
6041 cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col][tile_sb_row].start);
6042 assert(tok - cpi->tplist[tile_row][tile_col][tile_sb_row].start <=
6043 get_token_alloc(MI_BLOCK_SIZE >> 1, tile_mb_cols));
6044
6045 (void)tile_mb_cols;
6046}
6047
6048void vp9_encode_tile(VP9_COMP *cpi, ThreadData *td, int tile_row,
6049 int tile_col) {
6050 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
6051 const int tile_cols = 1 << cm->log2_tile_cols;
6052 TileDataEnc *this_tile = &cpi->tile_data[tile_row * tile_cols + tile_col];
6053 const TileInfo *const tile_info = &this_tile->tile_info;
6054 const int mi_row_start = tile_info->mi_row_start;
6055 const int mi_row_end = tile_info->mi_row_end;
6056 int mi_row;
6057
6058 for (mi_row = mi_row_start; mi_row < mi_row_end; mi_row += MI_BLOCK_SIZE)
6059 vp9_encode_sb_row(cpi, td, tile_row, tile_col, mi_row);
6060}
6061
6062static void encode_tiles(VP9_COMP *cpi) {
6063 VP9_COMMON *const cm = &cpi->common;
6064 const int tile_cols = 1 << cm->log2_tile_cols;
6065 const int tile_rows = 1 << cm->log2_tile_rows;
6066 int tile_col, tile_row;
6067
6068 vp9_init_tile_data(cpi);
6069
6070 for (tile_row = 0; tile_row < tile_rows; ++tile_row)
6071 for (tile_col = 0; tile_col < tile_cols; ++tile_col)
6072 vp9_encode_tile(cpi, &cpi->td, tile_row, tile_col);
6073}
